And the model for all of these has always

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:15.943
been multi-exemplary Norway.

00:18:16.930 --> 00:18:18.750
Norway good.

00:18:18.750 --> 00:18:21.490
Norway is Kuwait done right.

00:18:21.490 --> 00:18:24.224
- Because Norway had oil--

00:18:24.224 --> 00:18:28.270
- Oil money piling up, and
