all your normal business
would be destroyed

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:43.560
in terms of competitive,
and you have a mess.

00:18:43.560 --> 00:18:45.750
This used to be called the Dutch disease.

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:48.490
- Because the Dutch had
gone through this experience

00:18:48.490 --> 00:18:51.000
in the '60, they had some oil,

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:53.950
they generated a lot of money
and they blew it all away.

00:18:53.950 --> 00:18:56.993
- It did them no good, the opposite.

00:18:57.860 --> 00:19:01.109
So the Norwegians simply
said, we're putting it all

00:19:01.109 --> 00:19:04.230
in a bank account offshore.

00:19:04.230 --> 00:19:05.940
Because you bring it onshore, it raises it

00:19:05.940 --> 00:19:07.490
and we'll live on the interest.

00:19:08.360 --> 00:19:11.720
- And the money is in another currency,

00:19:11.720 --> 00:19:12.940
the dollar in this case?

