00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:58.140
of the neoliberal paradigm

00:26:58.140 --> 00:27:01.640
which dominated both political parties

00:27:01.640 --> 00:27:05.200
and which was embraced by
both Reagan and Clinton

00:27:05.200 --> 00:27:06.520
and the Bushes.

